usage: super [-h] [-l {1,4}] [-c] [-t {c,d}] [-g] [-s h k l] poscar

Manipulates VASP POSCAR files

positional arguments:
  poscar                filename of the VASP POSCAR to be processed

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -l {1,4}, --label {1,4}
                        label coordinates with atom name at position {1,4}
  -c, --coordinates-only
                        only output coordinates
  -t {c,d}, --coordinate-type {c,d}
                        specify coordinate type for output {c|d}
  -g, --group           group atoms within supercell
  -s h k l, --supercell h k l
                        construct supercell by replicating (h,k,l) times along
                        [a b c]
